div.p:
(1) Your November 24, midnight, and December 8, 3 p.m., from Nanking, regarding the question of alleged Chinese promises to withdraw
from Chinchow. I have asked the Embassy in Japan to repeat to you the essential parts of my 262, December 11, 9 p.m., to Tokyo,
Foreign Relations, Japan, 1931–1941, vol. i, p. 62. relating to this matter.
